WEBVTT

00:02:58.668 --> 00:03:01.893
You are more the incredible
shrinking woman

00:03:01.917 --> 00:03:05.840
than the Buddhist mystic,
serene, making do with less.

00:03:05.864 --> 00:03:08.645
Less is not always more.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:14.140
Yet in this emptying space,
space glimmers,

00:03:14.164 --> 00:03:15.798
becoming visible.

00:03:16.115 --> 00:03:19.474
Here is a place behind the eyes
of those accustomed

00:03:19.498 --> 00:03:22.767
by what some would call diminishment.

00:03:23.468 --> 00:03:27.143
It is a place of merciless poetry,

00:03:27.167 --> 00:03:30.486
a gift of presence previously ignored,